  {
    q: "When should we launch campaigns for summer holiday packages?",
    a: "For summer packages (April to June), campaigns should go live by mid-February so you have 8 weeks to build awareness and capture early planners. Parents in Ahmedabad start thinking about summer trips in March. If you wait until April your competitors have already taken the early bookings."
