  },
  {
    q: "How does the WhatsApp booking integration work?",
    a: "We create a booking enquiry form on your website that captures name, phone, destination interest, and travel dates. On submission it triggers a WhatsApp message to your sales number with all the details. Alternatively we use a direct WhatsApp button with a pre-filled message template so the client can start a conversation instantly."
  },
  {
    q: "Can you build specific landing pages for pilgrimage tours like Ambaji or Somnath darshan packages?",
    a: "Absolutely. We build dedicated pages for each pilgrimage destination: Ambaji, Somnath, Dwarka, Char Dham, Shirdi, and others. Each page has a relevant title for Google, full route information, departure dates, pricing, and a booking form. These pages attract organic traffic from people searching specifically for these packages."
  },
  {
    q: "How long does it take to start getting online bookings after you start working with us?",
    a: "Google Ads will start delivering enquiries within the first week if campaigns are set up with good landing pages. Organic SEO takes longer, usually 3 to 5 months before meaningful traffic builds. We typically run both together so you get immediate results from ads while SEO grows in the background."
